    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a rigorous professional inspection to ensure peak performance and aesthetic excellence. Offering a seamless blend of luxury and durability, it represents an exceptional acquisition for the discerning driver seeking both long-term value and distinction. Experience the assurance of a vehicle prepared to our exacting dealership standards.",
      "price": 36500.0,
